posting_body: ['Stay Warm in Your New Home!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Station Nine', '16720 6th Ave W , Lynnwood, WA, 98037', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 958 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'NEWLY Renovated homes..', 'GET EXCITED TO SHARE THE UNIQUE CHARM AND QUALITY of our apartment homes at an affordable price.', 'Experience the beauty in hot air balloon country and SkyKomish River.', 'Perfect location will ensure you a quick commute.', 'You will be proud to call Station 9 your new home.', 'Features', '- Full size washer/dryer', '- Storage', '- Open kitchens', '- Private decks/patios', '- Wood burning fireplaces with Mantel', 'Community Amenities', '- Wi-Fi', '- Club House', '- Outdoor Pool', '- 24-hr Fitness Center', '- Cable/Satellite', '- Pool Side BBQ', '- Covered Outdoor Seating w/ Fireplace', '- Playground', 'Pet Policy', 'Qualified pets welcome', 'Driving Directions', 'From I-5, take the 164th St. S.W. exit (#183).', 'Turn East onto 164th St. S.W. and drive about 3/4 of a mile to 6th Ave.', 'W and turn right.', 'Station 9 is ahead on the right.', 'Office Hours', 'Mon, Wed, Fri: 9:00am-6:00pm', 'Tue, Thur: 10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday 10:00am-5:00pm', 'Sunday - Closed', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'ghl9fR1sJrY']
